passages.text:
{"background": "classroom", "character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor"}
Welcome to Melody of Hearts! This is a guide on how to play the rhythm game sections of the game. (Press Enter to Advance Text)
[[Next->Explanation1]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor", "startBeatmap": "levels/tutorial/winter_wind_1.beatmap"}
There are 4 rows of rhythm arrows that you must hit with your arrow keys along with the beats of the music. Try it out!
[[Next->TutorialBeatmap1]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor"}
What a great performance! You have a knack for this.
[[Next->Explanation2]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor"}
Needs a little work. It's okay, we all need practice to get better.
[[Next->Explanation2]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor"}
Now here comes the fun part. Here are two choices that you pick - notice the colour. To choose one of the options, you simply play the arrows corresponding to that color, and disregard arrows of the other color.
[[Next->Explanation3]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor"}
Note that no matter which one you choose, you must play the non-colored arrows as well as possible. Scores are calculated by only counting the arrows that you chose plus the white arrows, so don't worry about not playing the other set.
[[Next->Explanation4]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor", "startBeatmap": "levels/tutorial/winter_wind_2.beatmap"}
Now try making a choice for yourself!
[[Next->TutorialBeatmap2]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor"}
You chose yellow! I like that color too.
[[Next->Explanation5]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor"}
You chose blue! A great color, if I do say so myself.
[[Next->Explanation5]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor", "emotion": "angry"}
You played both choices. You're supposed to play just one...
[[Next->Explanation5]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor", "emotion": "angry"}
You failed to select a choice. Try to score higher by getting more arrows correct!
[[Next->Explanation5]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor", "startBeatmap": "levels/tutorial/winter_wind_boss.beatmap"}
Alright, now that you're familiar with the game, here's the rest of this level for you to practice.
[[Next->TutorialBeatmap3]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor"}
Color me impressed! You were able to pass that monstrosity?
[[Next->Explanation7]]

{"character": "Prof. H", "portraitName": "professor"}
I guess we can't all be geniuses. A good effort, though.
[[Next->Explanation7]]
